article.description: — Matt Knowling had 15 points in Yale's 95-36 victory against Colby-Sawyer on Friday night.
article.headline: Yale secures 95-36 victory over Colby-Sawyer
article.story: NEW HAVEN, Conn. -- — Matt Knowling had 15 points in Yale's 95-36 victory against Colby-Sawyer on Friday night. Knowling shot 6 of 7 from the field and 3 for 4 from the line for the Bulldogs (6-5). Casey Simmons scored 12 points, going 5 of 6 from the field. Danny Wolf shot 4 of 7 from the field to finish with 10 points. Chaz Cullum led the Chargers in scoring, finishing with eight points. Jaisan Parker added six points and two steals for Colby-Sawyer. In addition, Bullen Taban had four points. Yale visits Quinnipiac in its next matchup on Monday. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
